(secondQuint)A Study of the Safety of IMOVAX Polio in China.

 Study participants will receive a single dose of IMOVAX Polio cent vaccine at 2, 3, and 4 months of age, respectively.

 Each participant will make a total of 7 visits.

 Safety will be monitored at each visit and up to 30 days after each vaccination.

